Package elki.evaluation.scores.adapter

Class DistanceResultAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • elki.evaluation.scores.adapter.DistanceResultAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ScoreEvaluation.Adapter, Iter
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FilteredDistanceResultAdapter
    public class DistanceResultAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements ScoreEvaluation.Adapter
    This adapter is used to process a list of (double, DBID) objects. The list must be sorted appropriately, the score is only used to detect ties.
    Since:
    0.7.0
    Author:
    Erich Schubert
